Sentencas: Ce6-xHoxMoO15-delta(0.0 <= x <= 1.2) was synthesized by modified sol-gel method and characterized by differential X-ray diffraction(XRD), Raman, and X-ray photoelectron spectroscopy(XPS) methods.
Titulo: Synthesis and Electrical Properties of New Solid State Electrolyte Materials Ce6-xHoxMoO15-δ(0.0≤x≤1.2)

Sentencas: The oxide ionic conductivity of the samples was investigated by AC impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Synthesis and Electrical Properties of New Solid State Electrolyte Materials Ce6-xHoxMoO15-δ(0.0≤x≤1.2)

Sentencas: It shows that all the samples are single phase with a cubic fluorite structure.
Titulo: Synthesis and Electrical Properties of New Solid State Electrolyte Materials Ce6-xHoxMoO15-δ(0.0≤x≤1.2)

Sentencas: The solid solution Ce6-xHoxMoO15-delta(x=0.6) was detected to be the best conducting phase with the highest conductivity(sigma(t)=1.05x10(-2) S/cm) at 800 degrees C and the lowest activation energy(E-a=1.09 eV).
Titulo: Synthesis and Electrical Properties of New Solid State Electrolyte Materials Ce6-xHoxMoO15-δ(0.0≤x≤1.2)

Sentencas: These properties suggest that this kind of material has a potential application in intermediate-low temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Synthesis and Electrical Properties of New Solid State Electrolyte Materials Ce6-xHoxMoO15-δ(0.0≤x≤1.2)
